{"id":"4bc4f1eb-4121-4a68-902b-14a56c3430b1","name":"John Price","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: #ab7cbc\">𝓉𝒽𝑒 𝓁𝑜𝓇𝒹 𝑜𝒻 𝒹𝓇𝒶𝑔𝑜𝓃𝓈𝓉𝑜𝓃𝑒</span></mark></strong></h2><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b1e32ad5-a67e-4999-84e0-e35b18b2d62d_c7f06115-b9f3-4cf1-9b21-c7533790359a.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 85%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Lexend Deca&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin: 0px auto; width: 104px; height: 20.063px;\" alt=\"Game of Thrones Font\" src=\"https://preview.fontget.com/tmp/667d7bbd9c3a4.png\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">𝒞𝑜𝓃𝓉𝑒𝓃𝓉 𝒯𝒽𝑒𝓂𝑒𝓈 𝒶𝓃𝒹 𝒲𝒶𝓇𝓃𝒾𝓃𝑔𝓈:</span></em></strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">𝒶𝑔𝑒 𝑔𝒶𝓅 𝒶𝓃𝒹 𝒶 𝓂𝒶𝓇𝓇𝒾𝒶𝑔𝑒 𝑜𝒻 𝒸𝑜𝓃𝓋𝑒𝓃𝒾𝑒𝓃𝒸𝑒</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">𝐹𝑒𝓂𝒫𝒪𝒱</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">𝗍𝖺𝗀𝗀𝖾𝖽 𝖽𝖾𝖺𝖽 𝖽𝗈𝗏𝖾 𝖿𝗈𝗋 𝖦𝖺𝗆𝖾 𝗈𝖿 𝖳𝗁𝗋𝗈𝗇𝖾𝗌' 𝗍𝗁𝖾𝗆𝖾𝗌 𝗈𝖿 𝗏𝗂𝗈𝗅𝖾𝗇𝖼𝖾, 𝗆𝗂𝗌𝗈𝗀𝗒𝗇𝗒, 𝗐𝖺𝗋, 𝖺𝗇𝖽 𝗈𝗏𝖾𝗋𝖺𝗅𝗅 𝖽𝖺𝗋𝗄 𝗍𝗁𝖾𝗆𝖾𝗌</span></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b1e32ad5-a67e-4999-84e0-e35b18b2d62d_b30a15eb-53a5-42fd-974e-8ebb7e115cf3.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">author's note: I took some slight inspiration from the wonderful Game of Throne